; The Sun Gate. The world's edge. Marduk passed through here and left
; what came after. The Sixth Master sends pilgrims here. The Seventh
; meets them. The Seventh Master himself spawns via NPCRoster (he is
; visibility-gated on the seventh_breath_pilgrimage_done flag).
;
; Atmosphere: noon-pale, blinding-white, sourceless light. No shadows.
; The gate itself is implied: a circular stone arch wider than three
; men can span. Wind that does not move the dust.
;
; Palette: noon-white · pale gold · faintest blue-shadow

